    "course_title": "ELEMENTARY MATRIX AND LINEAR ALGEBRA",
    "description": "An introduction to linear algebra. Topics include matrix algebra, linear systems of equations, vector spaces, sub-spaces, linear dependence, span, basis, rank of matrices, determinants, linear transformations, coordinate representations, kernel, range, eigenvalues and eigenvectors, diagonalization, inner products and orthogonal vectors, symmetric matrices. Covers linear algebra topics in greater depth and detail thanMATH\u00a0320. Formal techniques in mathematical argument [MATH\u00a0341] not covered.",
